title: Richard Cheese Discography (2000 - 2013)
description:
This is a torrent of the discography of Richard Cheese, including following:

Studio albums:
-2000 Lounge Against the Machine
-2002 Tuxicity
-2004 I'd Like a Virgin
-2005 Aperitif for Destruction
-2006 The Sunny Side of the Moon: The Best of Richard Cheese
-2006 Silent Nightclub
-2007 Dick at Nite
-2010 OK Bartender
-2010 Lavapalooza
-2011 A Lounge Supreme
-2012 Back In Black Tie
-2013 The Royal Baby Album
-2013 Cocktails With Santa

Live albums:
-2009 Viva la Vodka
-2011 Richard Cheese Live at the Royal Wedding

Singles:
-2011 Friday
